<section class="care-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="care-heading reveal">
      <svg class="heading-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 3 C9 7.5 6 11 6 14.5 C6 18 8.7 20 12 20 C15.3 20 18 18 18 14.5 C18 11 15 7.5 12 3 Z"/></svg>
      About Your Necklaces
    </h2>
    <p class="care-intro reveal">Both necklaces are crafted from 316L surgical-grade stainless steel — one of the most skin-safe and durable metals used in jewelry. The gold version features an 18K Gold PVD (Physical Vapor Deposition) finish: a process that bonds real gold to the steel at a molecular level, making it far more durable than standard gold plating.</p>

    <div class="care-icons reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="icon-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M12 3 C9 7.5 6 11 6 14.5 C6 18 8.7 20 12 20 C15.3 20 18 18 18 14.5 C18 11 15 7.5 12 3 Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Hypoallergenic</h4>
        <p>Safe for sensitive and reactive skin</p>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 3l1.2 3.4L17 7.5l-3.4 1.2L12 12l-1.2-3.3L7 7.5l3.8-1.1L12 3z"/><path d="M19 13l.7 2 2 .7-2 .7-.7 2-.7-2-2-.7 2-.7.7-2z"/><path d="M5 14l.6 1.7 1.7.6-1.7.6L5 18.6l-.6-1.7-1.7-.6 1.7-.6.6-1.7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Tarnish-Resistant</h4>
        <p>Keeps its shine with simple care</p>
      </div>
      <div class="icon-card">
        <div class="icon-circle">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M3 16c1.5-2 3.5-2 5 0s3.5 2 5 0 3.5-2 5 0 1.5 2 1.5 2"/><path d="M3 11c1.5-2 3.5-2 5 0s3.5 2 5 0 3.5-2 5 0 1.5 2 1.5 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Water-Resistant</h4>
        <p>Fine for hand washing and light rain</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="care-section" style="background:var(--blush);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="care-heading reveal">
      <svg class="heading-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
      Everyday Wear
    </h2>
    <p class="care-intro reveal">Your necklaces are designed to be worn daily. A few simple habits will keep them looking beautiful for years:</p>

    <ul class="checklist reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Put your necklace on last</strong> — after applying perfume, lotion, and hairspray.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Remove before sleeping</strong> — prevents chain kinking and tangling overnight.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Fine in the shower</strong> — the steel is water-resistant, though towel-dry after.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4"><path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Safe for hand washing</strong> — everyday soap and water won't harm the finish.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="care-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="care-heading reveal">
      <svg class="heading-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><path d="M4 12c1.5-5 4.5-8 8-8s6.5 3 8 8c-1.5 5-4.5 8-8 8s-6.5-3-8-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2.3"/></svg>
      How to Clean
    </h2>

    <div class="clean-grid reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <div class="clean-col">
        <h4>Quick Daily Clean</h4>
        <p>After each wear, gently wipe your necklace with a soft, dry microfiber or lint-free cloth. This removes skin oils and keeps the metal bright.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="clean-col">
        <h4>Deeper Clean (Monthly)</h4>
        <ol class="step-list">
          <li>Mix a few drops of mild dish soap in warm water.</li>
          <li>Dip a soft toothbrush and gently scrub the chain and charm.</li>
          <li>Rinse thoroughly under warm water.</li>
          <li>Pat dry with a soft cloth. Air dry completely before storing.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="care-section" style="background:var(--blush);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="care-heading reveal">
      <svg class="heading-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg>
      What to Avoid
    </h2>

    <ul class="avoid-list reveal reveal-delay-1">
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5"/><line x1="6.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.5" y2="17.5"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Harsh chemicals</strong> — bleach, chlorine pools, acetone (nail polish remover), and household cleaners can strip the PVD finish.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5"/><line x1="6.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.5" y2="17.5"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Perfume &amp; hairspray directly on the necklace</strong> — always apply these first, then put on your jewelry.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5"/><line x1="6.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.5" y2="17.5"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Abrasive materials</strong> — rough cloths, scrubbing pads, or baking soda can scratch the surface.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5"/><line x1="6.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.5" y2="17.5"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Hot tubs and prolonged pool submersion</strong> — extended chlorine exposure can dull the gold finish over time.</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="item-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="8.5"/><line x1="6.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.5" y2="17.5"/></svg></span>
        <span><strong>Ultrasonic cleaners</strong> — the vibration can loosen the crystal charm setting.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="care-closing reveal">Questions? We are here for you — <a href="mailto:support@lilytily.com" style="color:var(--rose-gold);">support@lilytily.com</a></p>
